  "name": "AI Document Automation (v2 - much better)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 1. INGEST\nWatches the Inbox folder, downloads the new file, and computes a SHA-256 hash + metadata used for logging and audit.",
        "height": 300,
        "width": 380
      },
      "id": "n1-5l61u2",
      "position": [
        -1200,
        -416
      ],
      "name": "Sticky - Ingestion",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 2. AI EXTRACTION + CLASSIFICATION\nOne multimodal model call replaces \"OCR engine -> separate classifier\". The model reads the file directly and returns strict, schema-validated JSON: department, confidence, summary, structured entities, sensitivity flag, priority. No free-text guessing - output is contractually shaped.",
        "height": 300,
        "width": 420
      },
      "id": "n2-7qtaas",
      "position": [
        -768,
        -416
      ],
      "name": "Sticky - AI",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 3. CONFIDENCE / SENSITIVITY GATE\nIf the AI call failed to parse, confidence < 75%, the doc is flagged sensitive, or it landed in \"Unclassified\" - it goes to a human review queue instead of auto-sending. Nothing sensitive or low-confidence gets auto-emailed.",
        "height": 300,
        "width": 420
      },
      "id": "n3-ubs58s",
      "position": [
        -304,
        -416
      ],
      "name": "Sticky - Gate",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## REVIEW PATH\nLogged to ReviewQueue, admin is alerted by email, file is moved to \"Needs Review\" - nothing is auto-sent to a department.",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 360
      },
      "id": "n4-xind7d",
      "position": [
        -736,
        352
      ],
      "name": "Sticky - Review Path",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## AUTO-SEND PATH\nRecipient + tone come from the DepartmentRouting sheet (edit that sheet to change who gets what - no workflow edits needed). Email is grounded in the extracted facts only. Logged to ProcessedLog, file moved to \"Processed\".",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 420
      },
      "id": "n5-27a24l",
      "position": [
        -1200,
        336
      ],
      "name": "Sticky - Auto Path",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
